msgstr "6. Cổ tức, lợi nhuận đã trả cho chủ sở hữu"

#. module: l10n_vn_b03dn_direct_report
#: model_terms:l10n.vn.b03dn.line,name:l10n_vn_b03dn_direct_report.b03dn_line_06
msgid "6. Other cash receipts from operating activities"
